m\nH$\\alpha$ observations of high redshift galaxies with complex morphologies, we\ncaution against analytical models that attempt to explain the SFR-$\\sigma_{\\rm\ng}$ relation without accounting for these effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2021 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 May 2022 18:09:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
