ection events around cool stars. We further propose that the measured\nvariations in grain sizes could directly be used to identify the presence of\nthe RDIs in close by systems with observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2021 19:00:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
