-art BVQA performance on 360{\\textdegree} video over two datasets,\nthe code of which has been public in\n\\url{https://github.com/yanglixiaoshen/ProVQA.}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Nov 2021 03:45:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-19"}
