ies performed on M-dwarf\nstars, focusing on how emerging signatures in different wavelengths related to\nthese events vary as a function of the magnetic properties of the star.\nFinally, the implications and relevance of these numerical results are\ndiscussed in the context of future characterization of host star-exoplanet\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Nov 2021 14:09:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
